comments: Zeller (CHA) and Washington (CHA) make marginal contact with Jokic (DEN) during his shot attempt at the rim.
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harris (DEN) and does not deliver contact.
Zeller (CHA) grabs the rim and causes the ball to take an unnatural bounce.
Zeller (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position on Jokic (DEN) during the drive.
The shot is imminent when Jokic (DEN) is in the lane for three seconds.
Washington (CHA) jumps from A to B into the body of Grant (DEN) and affects his shot attempt at the basket.
Barton (DEN) makes contact to the arm of Graham (CHA) and affects his driving shot attempt.
Graham (CHA) makes contact to the body of Barton (DEN) that affects his SQBR.
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harris (DEN) and does not deliver contact.
Grant (DEN) makes contact to the ball with his hand/arm, dislodging it from Zeller's (CHA) control before making any additional incidental contact to his arm.
Washington (CHA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Grant (DEN) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Rozier (CHA) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
